            <thetext>The qx.Mobile Picker should use the qx.ui.mobile.container.Scroll, the qx.Mobile list and the all-new waypoints feature.

Benefits:

Maintainability:
* Less code, re-using of known widgets.
* The dialog menu could be replaced in this case.

Usability: 
* The scrolling would provide a momentum


The picker should provide the same API as before, but internally use different qx.mobile widgets instead of a complete own implementation.</thetext>
